---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 4em 2em;
			}
			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3em;
			}
			.hero h1 {
				font-size: 3rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.3em;
			}
			.tagline {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				margin-bottom: 2em;
			}
			.intro {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
				margin-bottom: 2.5em;
			}
			.links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1em;
				justify-content: center;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
			}
			.links a {
				padding: 0.6em 1.4em;
				border-radius: 8px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: opacity 0.2s;
			}
			.links a:hover {
				opacity: 0.8;
			}
			.btn-primary {
				background: var(--accent);
				color: white;
			}
			.btn-secondary {
				border: 2px solid var(--accent);
				color: var(--accent);
			}
			hr {
				margin: 3em 0;
				border: none;
				border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			}
			.rebuild-note {
				text-align: center;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				font-style: italic;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero">
				<h1>PRISVALIS</h1>
				<p class="tagline">
					<span data-zh>王老師生命專線</span>
					<span data-en>Albert Wang's Tech Blog</span>
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="intro">
				<span data-en>
					<p>Hi, I'm <strong>Albert Wang</strong>, a Computer Science student at <strong>Feng Chia University</strong> in Taiwan.</p>
					<p>I'm passionate about <strong>embedded systems, cloud and edge computing, and AI-driven system integration</strong>. I currently work as a System Engineer at <strong>imCloud Co., Ltd.</strong>, building data ingestion pipelines, device control logic, and IoT edge collaboration systems.</p>
					<p>This is where I document my technical projects, server setups, and anything else I find worth sharing.</p>
				</span>
				<span data-zh>
					<p>嗨，我是 <strong>Albert Wang</strong>，目前就讀於 <strong>逢甲大學資訊工程學系</strong>。</p>
					<p>我對 <strong>嵌入式系統、雲端與邊緣運算、AI 應用整合</strong> 充滿熱情。目前在 <strong>機智雲股份有限公司</strong> 擔任系統工程師，負責資料接收流程、設備控制邏輯與 IoT 邊緣協同架構的開發。</p>
					<p>這裡記錄我的技術專案、伺服器架設筆記，以及一切值得分享的東西。</p>
				</span>
			</div>

			<div class="links">
				<a href="/blog" class="btn-primary">
					<span data-en>Read the Blog</span>
					<span data-zh>瀏覽文章</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/about" class="btn-secondary">
					<span data-en>About Me</span>
					<span data-zh>關於我</span>
				</a>
			</div>

			<hr />

			<p class="rebuild-note">
				<span data-en>This is the 10th rebuild of this site — officially recorded. WOW.</span>
				<span data-zh>這是我第 10 次（官方紀錄）重建這個網站 WOW。</span>
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
